c: 9
v: 101
t: "Ne mubabedui barulanga mumbeka mwenyu mutsingongo tsili ahambi ninanyu, khulimwo nende abeshikhabili, nende mubamenyanwa ba Madina, beyibila mubushikhabili, obakorerwe ne efwe khwabamanya. Khwitsa okhubasandia mara khabili, mana balikalusibwa okhutsia okhusandibwa eshinyasio eshikhongo"